data.description:
Beautiful home south of I-10! 3 bedroom 2 bathroom with formal dining room plus a HUGE bonus room above the garage that could be used as a 4th bedroom! Fenced in backyard and zoned for great schools!

Renters are responsible for all utilities and must have renters insurance. 
Animals allowed with a fee. 
Absolutely no smoking in the house.
Must make 2.5x the rent. 
Must have a credit score of 600 or better. 
No prior evictions and have references for past rentals.
